                },
                {
                  "type": "tip",
                  "text": "S3 access should be done via IAM policies and roles.  Refer to the <a href=\"http://docs.aws.amazon.com/AmazonS3/latest/dev/intro-managing-access-s3-resources.html\">S3 Developer Guide</a>.",
